go_upc.name: Tate's Bake Shop Salted Caramel Chocolate Chip Cookies - 6.5oz
go_upc.description: Treat yourself to a bake shop quality snack with Tate's Bake Shop Salted Caramel Chocolate Chip Cookies. Uniquely thin and deeply delicious, these kosher snack cookies are a buttery, sweet delight with salted caramel. The light, crisp texture makes these cookies a perfect sweet treat for savoring for yourself or sharing with friends in a cookies bag or cookies gift box. These cookies also make great lunch snacks, and they're a sweet addition to other chocolate dessert recipes. They also are fantastic as a sweet treat, evening snacks, Easter basket fillers or as a treat during a summer picnic. Tate's Bake Shop cookies come in a resealable 6.5 ounce bag to keep each cookie crisp and fresh.
